{{codepointer|Special action}}'''A_ClassBossHealth'''

(no parameters)

Multiplies the health of the calling actor by 5 ''when'' playing cooperative and sets the calling actor {{c|special1}} field to 1, but only if it was equal to 0 beforehand. Otherwise it does nothing.

== Examples ==
This demon can heal itself when heavily wounded, but only once.

 Actor ToughDemon : {{class|Demon}}
 {
 	{{property|Health}}	500
 	{{property|WoundHealth}}	100
 	States
 	{
 		Wound:
 		"----" A 5 [[A_ClassBossHealth]]
 		goto See
 	}
 }
